### ============================================================
### BETTERLINK VENTURES — Co-op Balance Real-Time Test
### ============================================================
### HOW TO USE:
### 1. Replace YOUR_BASIC_AUTH_VALUE below with your Base64
###    encoded consumerKey:consumerSecret
### 2. Run "Step 1" first to get a token
### 3. Copy the access_token value from the response
### 4. Paste it as @token below
### 5. Run each step in order
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://openapi.co-opbank.co.ke
@basicAuth = c0NScXdOVlRrcTNDTzFUTTFOUHplSEhGcW0wYTpHa0NGQVJianZTa3U0dHluTDFqMlJlSjR1Smth
